headline: Cloudflare Integrations Marketplace introduces three new partners: Sentry, Momento and Turso
keywords: Birthday Week, Product News, Developers, Cloudflare Workers, Observability, Edge Database, Cache, Partners
description: Earlier this year, we introduced integrations with Supabase, PlanetScale, Neon and Upstash. Today, we are thrilled to introduce our newest additions to Cloudflare’s Integrations Marketplace – Sentry, Turso and Momento
